WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
GULF OF MEXICO.
MARYLAND TO FLORIDA.
DNC 15.
1. S/V MARIAH, BEIGE HULL WITH BLUE STRIPE, ONE PERSON
   ON BOARD, OVERDUE BALTIMORE (39-17.0N 076-37.0W)
   TO PANAMA CITY (30-10.5N 085-39.9W). VESSELS IN VICINITY
   REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF
   POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO U.S. COAST GUARD MIAMI,
   PHONE: 305 415 6800, E-MAIL: RCCMIAMI@USCG.MIL.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2702/14.
